+/**
+ * lwmi_psy_ext_get_prop() - Get a power_supply_ext property
+ * @ps: The battery that was extended
+ * @ext: The extension
+ * @ext_data: Pointer the lwmi_om_priv drvdata
+ * @prop: The property to read
